videos.description: Aicha Coulibaly get in for the layup and ties the game, recovering from an 8-point deficit against Georgia.

videos.description: Sania Wells creates the turnover, then sinks two free throws in the final seconds to secure Auburn's win over No. 21 Georgia.

videos.headline: Sania Wells' clutch play seals win for Auburn

videos.description: Behind Honesty Scott-Grayson's 23 points, the Tigers pull away with a tight 65-60 upset against No. 21 Georgia.
videos.headline: Auburn records third win over Top 25 team this season
